	* macosx/tkMacOSXCarbonEvents.c:	fix debug carbon event tracing;
	(InstallStandardApplicationEventHandler):	replace needless use of
	TkMacOSXInitNamedDebugSymbol() by standard TkMacOSXInitNamedSymbol().

