	* macosx/tkMacOSXFont.c (TkpMeasureCharsInContext): Fix short measures
	with flags=TK_WHOLE_WORDS|TK_AT_LEAST_ONE [Bug 1716141]. Make some
	casts unnecessary by changing variable types.

