	******************************************************************
	*** CHANGELOG ENTRIES FOR 2004 AND 2003 IN "ChangeLog.2004"    ***
	*** CHANGELOG ENTRIES FOR 2002 AND EARLIER IN "ChangeLog.2002" ***
	******************************************************************
